# nvflsh64.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png)  ![:inline](/images/elmo.gif) 

### Description

nvflsh64.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: d4664202-d1b9-44d4-97cc-fee2150082db
- **Created**: 2023-01-09
- **Author**: Michael Haag
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/d3e40644a91327da2b1a7241606fe559.bin" "Download" >}}{{< button "https://www.magicsword.io/premium" "Block" "red" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create nvflsh64.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp \n \n \n  vflsh64.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start nvflsh64.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
